      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it's a debate, but can u be more specific? like, when people talk about 'originalism' vs 'living constitution' in this context, is one of those approaches actually more grounded in legal theory, or is it just a way for judges to push their own politics? i want to make sure i'm not just repeating biased talking points in my paper.",
